Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.85,0:01:11.85,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}为错位的焦点所惑 四下寻找说辞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.31,0:01:14.31,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}看吧枯叶起舞 终会化为蝴蝶
