Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.31,0:01:17.31,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,0)\blur2\be1}然后是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.40,0:01:21.40,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}时过境迁太急 秒速开始不合理
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.90,0:01:23.90,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}全因自己武断的选择开端
