Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.82,0:01:29.83,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}无聊的理由 是停止思考的铁证
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.12,0:01:33.12,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}无法守护应守护之物 那就不要乱出头
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.04,0:01:38.04,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}共鸣 荣光 称赞 都不应奢求
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.92,0:01:41.92,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}不明真相的引力 将常识归于虚无
