Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.94,0:02:00.94,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}全都变得讨厌 连这都是幸福的结局
